               <p>ANN KING. I am a <rs id="t18171203-26-viclabel154" type="occupation">laundress</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171203-26-victim248 t18171203-26-viclabel154"></join>. On the 28th of November, about five o'clock in the afternoon, I missed the things off my lines, and found the prisoner lying down in the wash-house with them - I laid hold of him - He got away, but was taken immediately.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
